node.title: Child hit by vehicle in Papakura
node.description: A child has been taken to hospital in critical condition after being hit by a vehicle in south Auckland.
node.content: ["A child has been taken to hospital in critical condition after being hit by a vehicle in south Auckland.", "Police said the incident on Elizabeth Street in the suburb of Papukura was reported shortly before 2.20pm.", "The road is currently closed and the Serious Crash Unit is investigating."]
